spec_data.Name: emacs-pymacs-el
spec_data.Description:
This package contains the elisp source files for pymacs under GNU Emacs. You
do not need to install this package to run emacs-pymacs. Install the emacs-pymacs
package to use pymacs with GNU Emacs.
